title: What can I help you with today?.

prompts.label: Find Opportunities
prompts.description: Create a list of producers who are most likely to submit a large case life or annuity policy within the next 30 days.

prompts.label: Agent Cross-Sell
prompts.description: Create a list of my producers who currently sell one product line (life or annuity), but are likely to sell more than one product line in the future.

prompts.label: Plan Follow-Ups
prompts.description: Create a list of producers who had cases pay within the last week, arranged by premium in descending order.

prompts.label: At-Risk Producers
prompts.description: Create a current list of my top producers by premium sold who are most at risk of leaving.

prompts.label: Future Top Producers
prompts.description: Create a list of my current producers who are most likely to achieve top producer status within the next two years.

prompts.label: Rising New Agents
prompts.description: Create a list of my producers contracted less than one year ago, who are likely to experience business growth of 30%*, year-over-year.

prompts.label: Producer Progression
prompts.description: Create a list of producers with next-step progression delays over 3 days

prompts.label: Engagement Data
prompts.description: Provide me with lists of producers that engage the most with our company's agent portal, attend our monthly agent trainings and attend our live company events, year to date.

prompts.label: Distribution Insights
prompts.description: Generate a report of my total year-to-date premium by sales organization versus their annual sales goal for each group, as well as the total amount of pending business for each group.

prompts.label: Trend Analysis
prompts.description: Create a line graph of my sales organizations' life and annuity premium sales over the last five years.

prompts.label: Create Sales Charts
prompts.description: Create a separate pie chart for each product type showing year-to-date sales by product.  Include a detailed breakdown of all life insurance and annuity products sold this year.
